data.description: Beautiful Well-kept 4 bedroom 2.5 bathroom home located in the Overhills Creek Subdivision. This home features luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout the downstairs and upstairs. Enjoy the mornings and evenings on the covered front porch.  Inside you have a formal dining room, kitchen (with view of living room), the living room, and half bath.  You also have your laundry room off the kitchen coming from your two-car garage.  At the top of the stairs you'll find the large owner suite with a corner for an office, the owners bathroom with separate shower, garden tub, and walk-in closet.  You also have two other bedrooms, with the second upstairs bathroom. At the end of the hall is the Bonus room with two oversized closets (bonus is 4th bedroom) and it's own office/closed loft off the side of the bonus room. Large patio overlook the fully fenced back yard.
